Getting redhead brigand's stuff
A rumor is afoot that one of the brigands, the Redhead, meets with the Orcs and engages in friendly conversation with them. Perhaps something among his possessions could prove that yet another person in the village also deals with the Orcs?
#subobj  1
Find the Redhead
The redhead Brigand who talked to an Orc has been seen near the camp of the Brigands, in an easterly direction across the river. There you find a road which leads to the cave in the mountains.....
#subobj  2
Kill the Redhead
The traitor must be killed.
#subobj  3
Search the Redhead
Mayhap there is something of interest among his belongings.....
